huli hebbuli ( kannada : ಹುಲಿ ಹೆಬ ಬುಲಿ ) is a 1987 kannada action film directed by vijay and written by shanmuga sundaram . the film starred shankar nag , tiger prabhakar , sumalatha and bhavya in the lead roles.ananth nag played a brief guest appearance role . the film was produced by b. nagi reddy . the film 's score and songs were composed by vijaya bhaskar to the lyrics of chi . udaya shankar . the cinematography was by s. ramachandra .